What is programing language?
Answer: Programming languages are used in computer programming to create programs that implement specific algorithms.


What jdk contains or composed of and define each components?
Answer: it contains the Java Virtual Machine (JVM)

   Components are:
   	The Runtime Interpreter
   	The Compiler
   	The Applet Viewer
   	The Debugger
   	The Class File Disassembler
   	The Header and Stub File Generator
   	The Documentation Generator
   	Applet Demos
   	API Source Code


